Selenium 
	It is a functional testing
	Test only web based applications.(Related to web browser) 
	
	Components of Selenium Suite

	1. Selenium IDE
		-->Record and playback feature(no writing script).
		-->Plugin to browsers: Firefox and Chrome.
	2. Selenium RC(outdated components)
		-->requires scripting
		-->problem: same origin policy (user in US and tester in Mumbai ...to access we have to establish in my location).
	3. Selenium Webdriver
		-->server is anywhere is tested easily
		-->requires scripting in following languages (JAVA,Pyton, Ruby, Groovy,JS,C#).
		--> supports cross browsers or mutli browsers testing (platform independent)
		-->support data driven testing framework,TDD(Junit),BDD,Keyword drievn ,hybrid driven.
	4. Selenium Grid
		-->can run selenium webdriven script on multiple systems at a time.(linux,windows,mac).
