--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

To locate the element on the web page we have to use Element Locators:
	driver.findElement(By.name(" "))
Element Locators:
1.Name
2.id
	Above element locators are directly available as as "tag attributes".
3.xpath
4.cssSelector
5.tagNmae
6.className
7.linkTest
8.partialLinkTest
